text: Solveig Skaugvoll Foss (born 5 December 1996) is a Norwegian politician for the Socialist Left Party. She serves as a deputy representative to the Parliament of Norway from Oslo during the term 2017-2021. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:politicians from Oslo Category:Deputy members of the Storting Category:Socialist Left Party (Norway) politicians Category:Norwegian women in politics
